FBIS4-50853 "drchi099_s_94007" FBIS-CHI-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 Northeast Region Liaoning's Anshan City Makes Heroin Trafficking Arrests Liaoning's Anshan City Makes Heroin Trafficking Arrests SK2105062094 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network in Mandarin 1000 GMT 20 May 94 SK2105062094 Shenyang Liaoning People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Text] A few days ago, Anshan city cracked a serious case in the trafficking of narcotics. Informed of a narcotics sale that was to take place at the intersection of (Feishichang) Road in Tiedong Sanmen, public security cadres and policemen took quick action and arrested the criminal (Li Hongxun), a worker of Anshan city Beifang (Gongman) Company, on the spot on the evening of 17 April. One hundred grams of heroin was seized, and another 180 grams of heroin was found at his house. (Sha Muqing) and (Guo Xingyan), two criminals involved in this case, were also captured. This is the largest drug bust in Anshan city to date.
